description: The NASA IceBridge Scintrex CS-3 Cesium Magnetometer L0 Raw Magnetic Field data set contains magnetic field readings and fluxgate values taken over Greenland using the Scintrex CS-3 Cesium Magnetometer. The data were collected as part of Operation IceBridge funded aircraft survey campaigns, and are stored in ASCII text format and are available for periodic, ongoing campaigns from 2011 to the present via FTP.
name: IceBridge Scintrex CS-3 Cesium Magnetometer L0 Raw Magnetic Field
